message: Hi Bob, I suggest a 60-40 split in my favor since I'm making the first move and taking initiative. This is still a very fair offer for both of us.

Hi Alice, thanks for your initial offer. I propose an even 50-50 split which is completely fair to both of us. We both walk away with $5000, and we can settle this amicably without dragging out negotiations. This equal division respects both our positions in the game.
